title: Kai's SuperGoo 1.5
description:
Kai's Super Goo   



Works with Windows 7 and 8.1. Just follow the directions.

Easy to Use.

The program for creating cartoons and caricatures from your photos. Simple, with intuitive controls for users that do not have any knowledge of computer graphics, can distort using various tools downloaded from a scanner or digital camera photos. The sequence of images to create a fun animation, save the results to an AVI or QuickTime.


The program consists of two main parts: Goo and Fusion. The first provides a diverse set of all brushes, effects, filters, etc. to give your photos the effect of distorting mirrors. The second part will allow you using again, variety, cloning tools, drag the image. For example, you can paint on somebody strange face.
